<span class="displaytext">(candidate full) made the following statement today regarding president bush's intention to nominate jim nussle to be the director of the office of management and budget: <p>"president bush made a great choice in jim nussle for director of the office of management and budget. the president's decision was the right one for our country and for taxpayers. </p><p>"jim and i have long shared a commitment to fiscal discipline and i have every confidence he will continue to be an effective steward of taxpayers' hard earned dollars in his new position. </p><p>"as our campaign continues to grow our team in iowa, i am grateful to jim for his early support and for his hard work in helping our team get started."</p></span>



